Winter 👉 Summer
Things that don’t change:
1. Semi naked levels 😅
2. Wearing red for extra engagement 
3. My diet & lifestyle -
Been asked a lot in the DMs recently what routine/ diet I have in place over Christmas hols.. I stare at these kind of messages veryyy blankly ngl. I have no plans to fast or drink weird green things or do cardio or go ‘extra hard’ in the gym as a result of taking time off. I plan to continue living my best life, a balanced one where I don’t restrict any food group. One where I train for enjoyment and feels. Push myself to test my mindset & challenge myself for growth. Let’s not over complicate things that don’t need to be. 
Ps. Find a lifestyle that suits you, don’t replicate the lifestyle of a random person you follow like a lemon (including myself). Okaybyeeee.
Pps. You can however choose to #staynutty. But it’s optional. No peer pressure going down on this account 🤙 #youdoyou #fitness #gains #bodypositive #feelingthered #realtalk

Spread love, eat churros for breakfast & be happy. 😌😚
-
Before we go any further with this caption I’d like to point out that that is not poor foundation application on my neck lol, issa shadow. I’m personally way too lazy to invest time into applying foundation. That said, I read a YouTube comment yesterday that said: ‘I’d look gorgeous IF I had a proper skincare, haircare routine & invested in good hair removal’ lol cheers for that Margaret. The thing is, I’m actually good. I know, it’s outrageous to be comfortable in our own skin. Then again, imagine being someone who takes on board the insignificant judgments of others & then feels the need to change themself in order to gain validation from that said tool?! Now that would be tragic. And it is. And it happens constantly. I’m not here to change the world with churros but then again maybe this will make you question how much of your attention you give to the belittlers that you could instead flick off in an instance. Just a thought xoxoxo 🥰
Ps. That’s thick hot choc in ze mug. Didn’t want to risk any potential choc wastage for the snap though, soz 😬
#churros #selflove #beyou #behappy #madrid #ibrushoffhatersnotmyhairlol

Lol to think this time last year, pretty much to this day.. I was on the verge of quitting both YouTube & IG because my bf at the time ..wait for it......(no really just wait..) wasn’t a fan of social media. Thankfully he wasn’t willing for me to give it up for him. But um kinda then leaves no ultimatum. Highkey devastating. Lowkey jealousy. (Actually probably the highest of keys jealousy*). That period of time actually really made me question myself for the first time. It made me seriouslyy consider if this platform was worth continuing with. I deliberated it for a good couple of days...then I came out with an absolute banger of a YouTube video titled ‘I put my soul into this video’. The thumbnail had 3 bold words all capitalised ‘THIS IS ME’. I may have cried at the time but I’m for sure the one smiling now. Never let anyone ever make you question your passion, especially when we out here working with fresh Nikes now, bish. Remember, there are levels. And you should never have to take a step down just so somebody else can try & catch up to you. Miaowww. 🤙😝
Ps. I know this story seems like it kinda came out of nowhere I know hahha - couple people dm’d me recently about getting over exes. I dedicate this post to you. xoxox
#startedfromthebottomnowwehere 
#youdoyou #realtalk #mood #motivation

If you really, reallyyy knew me, you’d know my real purpose in using this platform is not about receiving fire emojis on the pics I post. You’d know that my main objective is for us all to strive to be our best and live our best life. You’d know that I’ve absolutely zero shame in using my body to reach more people given it’s a visual platform, tbh I think I look peachy. You’d know I’m confident & comfortable in my own skin & want for us all to be in our own. You’d know that my quirky captions more often than not have deeeper connotations & you’d know that I’m on a mission to inspire ze nation. I just answered one of the 9 questions I am posting here from the podcast I listened to by @jayshetty about eliminating small talk & encouraging more meaningful convos. -
Pick a number, I dare you to answer it in the comments below. NO JUDGMENT ZONE. ❤️👇👇
1 What was the last lie you told, would you tell it again?
2 If you met your younger self today what would make them happy about you & what would make them sad about you?
3 What type of situation makes you feel awkward and why?
4 What did you buy recently that you now regret?
5 Have you ever been to jail or gotten arrested? 
6 What do you think makes a person most attractive? How attractive are you on that scale? 
7 If you really REALLY knew me, you’d know that ____________ .
8 What do you fight about most in your romantic relationship?
9 What would you talk about the most in a one hour therapy session? 
#purpose #impact #letstalkmore #mondaymotivation

Warning: This one may hurt 
#realtalk👇
Sometimes I hold back on things I want to say because I don’t want to come across too harsh or be too hard on you all. I don’t want to offend. I don’t want for people to feel guilt. But the fact of the matter is, the generation has gone way too soft. Excuses is all I hear. ‘But this’. ‘But that’. NO. Ok?! NO. Enough is enough!!! It’s December, it’s winter, it’s Christmas, it’s cold.. you think that’s going to stop me getting the shot for the gram on my way back home from my lidl food shop???!!! Hell no. It’s time to man up, & stop being all about our damn feelings!!! That said, I’ve lost all feeling in my fingers bye x
Ps. People walked by as I was taking this & for a good 26 ish odd seconds I feared for the shopping bags. It was at that moment I realised how little I cared for my coat & scarf. They can take it! Just. Stay. Away. From. My. Food!!!!! Pps. Editing new foodie video as we speak, stay tuned. I’m trying to make it happen. Subscribe in the mean time:
Nuttyfoodiefitness - hit the bell so you get notified when this banger of a video goes liveeeeee 😍🤙

When you’ve a goal you are out to achieve, let nothing get in your way. Even if it means, pushing a couple walls to a side. Then so be it. Whatever it takes. Too many people will just let things be. Hope for a perfect time to come. Sit back & watch how things pan out.. My friends, the only way that ends is with life passing you by. Before you know it, all the ‘coulda’ ‘wouldas’ end up being ‘I wish I’d have’, ‘if only’..
Mate, just go for it now. 
One life.
Go out & own it. 🔥
EDIT: TAG PEOPLE THAT NEED TO HEAR THIS!! I’m talking about those peeps you know that are dithering about starting xyz. Enough. Start now. Today. Ok. I’m done. Bye.
#mood #motivation #positivevibes #gains #fitness
